    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potato</strong> and <strong>chopped carrot</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 10-12 min or until fork-tender, then drain and return to the pot to steam dry and cool</p><p>Reboil a full kettle</p>",
